facts.fact: On May 27, 2019, Tri-Rail had a total ridership of 397,440 passengers.

Tri-Rail experienced a 4.2% increase in ridership compared to May 2018.
The end-to-end on-time performance (OTP) for Tri-Rail in May 2019 was 82.41%.
